
Instructions
------------

Download and build kitemmodels to run this:

    PFX=$PWD

    git clone http://anongit.kde.org/extra-cmake-modules
    cd extra-cmake-modules
    mkdir build && cd build
    cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=$PFX/opt/kf5
    cmake --build .
    cmake --build . --target install

    cd $PFX
    git clone http://anongit.kde.org/kitemmodels
    cd kitemmodels
    mkdir build && cd build
    cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=$PFX/opt/kf5
    cmake --build .
    cmake --build . --target install

    cd $PFX
    cd selection_grid
    mkdir build && cd build
    cmake .. -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH=$PFX/opt/kf5
    cmake --build .

    ./selection_grid
